protected void extractMessageData(IAeMessageData aMessageData)
                           throws AeBusinessProcessException
Extracts the message data into the variable and initiates or validates any correlation sets. If there are any errors during this process then an exception will be thrown or false returned indicating that the child activity shouldn't be executed.
